data.description: Welcome to this charming all-brick ranch, nestled on a beautiful corner lot in Cherryville. Quaint front porch. Light, bright & spacious interior. Remodeled kitchen w/stunning granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, gorgeous cabinets & stylish backsplash adds a touch of sophistication. Roof was recently replaced (5 years), ensuring peace of mind for years to come. Partially finished basement w/sitting area, oversized closet featuring barn door & cozy breakfast nook. Start your day by heading to the patio to enjoy your morning coffee amidst the serene surroundings in delightful presence of beautiful birds. Fenced-in yard offers ultimate privacy & relaxation w/hot tub for unwinding after a long day & refreshing pool for cooling off. Entertain on upper-level patio or gather around the fire pit for cozy evenings under the stars. Friendly neighbors & quiet neighborhood provide a welcoming atmosphere. Convenient proximity to shopping & schools. Come & see!
